            <h3>4. Palace of Versailles (Versailles)</h3>
            <p>The Palace of Versailles is a famous palace building and historical monument that has been
                become a world heritage site by UNESCO. In 2017, the Palace of Versailles received
                7.7 million visitors, making it the second most visited monument in the le-de-France region.
                In this famous tourist area, you will enjoy the beauty of the interior of the palace with golden colors and lights
                very beautiful hanging.
            </p>    
            
        </div>

